            Transferring groups other than aminoacyl groups
SYSNAME     acyl-CoA:glycine N-acyltransferase
REACTION    acyl-CoA + glycine = CoA + N-acylglycine [RN:R00395]
ALL_REAC    R00395 > R05841
SUBSTRATE   acyl-CoA [CPD:C00040];
            glycine [CPD:C00037]
